&lt;h2&gt;Gastroenterology Services Admin Manager&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Gastroenterology department at PHU is looking to appoint permanently to the role of Gastroenterology Services This role of Admin Manager will support all aspects of the service, inclusive of Gastroenterology, Hepatology and Endoscopy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an enthusiastic, motivated individual who enjoys working in a vibrant and growing service. You must have apassion for supporting the delivery of excellent patient-focused care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will work closely with the Service Floor Manager, Business Manager and clinical teams to promote efficient service delivery. In addition, you will be involved in thedetailed planning and implementation of change and willsupport the day to day running of the services function, being a key member of the administrative team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You should have experience of the national elective care access standards (18 weeks (RTT), cancer, diagnostic), engaging and supervising administrative functions and reviewing and improving administrative processes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details, please contact Kim Page 023 9228 6000 ext 5229.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Closing date: 11/11/2020&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
